room_title: Escape room "The Trick" by The Art of Escape: ICT in Wichita
review: We've done multiple rooms in multiple places around Wichita and this is by far the best! Their difficult room, the Trick, is really great. (We've got the second place time in that room!) We liked this business so much that we went through a room a week and now we'll have to wait until they get a new one so we can enjoy their mischief again. Definitely try them, you won't regret it.
